NAME
      kso -- code complexity analyser

SYNOPSIS
      kso [-c] [-f FILE] [-g] [-h] [-k] [-p] [-q] [-v]

DESCRIPTION
      Static code complexity analyser for c-family syntax (C, C++, Java, ECMAScript, C#, ...)
      it parses decisions of a standard data input stream (stdin) and calculates an absolute number.

      -c            cyclomatic complexity, condition count, O(n)
      -f, --file    read one or more newline separated patterns from file
      -g            control flow path conjecture, O(2n)
      -h, --help    show this help message
      -k            ksi complexity, regards nested c-family syntax, O(n^2)
      -p            ksi path vector
      -q            all sub paths, O(2^n)
      -v            verify condition paths
